###
### 2. Sign In - Login with existing user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign_in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###
### 3. Verify Token - Check if token is valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 4. Refresh Token - Get a new token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 5. Logout - User logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 6. Chat Route - Test protected chat route
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
